title: What God Left Out: Flatbread Faith
description: Sometimes, God’s provision isn’t in what He gives, but in what He leaves out. In “What God Left Out: Flatbread Faith,” Pastor Steven Furtick of Elevation Church reminds us that God is still in the details – even when we don’t understand them.
